-- Areva to Spend EU2 Bln to Secure Equipment, Handelsblatt Says
-- B y   J u l i e   C r u z
-- 2012-03-26T06:46:27Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-26/areva-to-spend-eu2-bln-to-secure-equipment-handelsblatt-says.html
Areva SA (CEI)  wants to spend eight
billion euros ($10.61 billion) to grow in the next five years,
including 2 billion euros to secure its equipment,  Handelsblatt 
reported, citing an interview with Chief Executive Officer Luc Oursel.  To contact the reporter on this story:
